data.description: This ranch-style house has over 1600 square feet of space, with three bedrooms and two bathrooms. The attached two-car garage provides convenient parking. The owner has lovingly cared for this home for 27 years. Inside, you'll find fresh new paint, giving it a modern and inviting feel. The house features a basement, perfect for extra storage or creating a cozy entertainment space. The new shadow boxing fencing adds a touch of elegance to the exterior. With a assumable loan  it's a great opportunity for buyers. You'll also find three storage sheds, perfect for all your storage needs. Enjoy the outdoors on the 12 by 12 deck, and keep your lawn looking lush with the sprinkler system. The newer furnace and AC ensure comfort all year round. This house has so much to offer, and I'm excited for you to share it with potential buyers!
